      "writtenOn": "2021-05-27T03:10:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s 256KB in the internal size.\nhttps://cloud.google.com/logging/quotas\n\nIt\u0027s not exactly the length of the wire byte representation, but http://shortn/_4HzvkeP7oQ\n\nThe size computation gets complicated when there are large label values. At the worst case, it\u0027d return an error, and Logdog should just ignore the error, as retries on the request will return the same error continuously.\n\nI added additional limits to minimize the chance of CloudLogging entries to be rejected due to the size. PTAL",
